INSERT INTO `attraction_metadata` VALUES (1,1,'{\"email\": {\"url\": \"mailto:info@amazeadam.nl\", \"value\": \"info@amazeadam.nl\"}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+31208510600\", \"value\": \"+31 20 851 0600\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"https://www.amaze-amsterdam.com/nl?utm_source=google&utm_medium=google_mijn_bedrijf&utm_campaign=link\", \"value\": \"www.amaze-amsterdam.com/nl?utm_source=google&utm_medium=google_mijn_bedrijf&utm_campaign=link\"}}','Amaze Amsterdam strives to be accessible. The experience is wheelchair friendly and has accessible restrooms. Some areas may have limited accessibility due to the nature of the experience, please contact them in advance for specific concerns.','All seasons, as it is an indoor attraction.','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"12:00\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": true, \"open_time\": null, \"close_time\": null}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"12:00\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"12:00\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"12:00\", \"close_time\": \"21:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"11:00\", \"close_time\": \"21:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"11:00\", \"close_time\": \"19:00\"}]','Amaze Amsterdam is an immersive, interactive audiovisual experience. Explore seven different rooms filled with cutting-edge technology, light, and sound. Discover a new dimension of entertainment in the heart of Amsterdam.',75,'[\"Navigate the mesmerizing world of light and sound.\", \"Experience the seven distinct rooms, each with a unique theme and atmosphere.\", \"Immerse yourself in the cutting-edge audiovisual technology.\", \"Discover interactive installations that react to your presence.\", \"Enjoy the DJ experience in a unique environment.\", \"Capture unforgettable moments with stunning photo opportunities.\", \"Engage with the multisensory environment.\", \"Explore the final room, a culmination of the Amaze journey.\"]','2025-12-11 10:32:43','2025-12-11 10:32:43'),(2,2,'{\"email\": {\"url\": \"mailto:info@lovers.nl\", \"value\": \"info@lovers.nl\"}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+31206791370\", \"value\": \"+31 20 679 1370\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"http://www.amsterdamcanalcruises.nl/\", \"value\": \"www.amsterdamcanalcruises.nl\"}}','Accessibility varies by boat. Some boats offer wheelchair access; it\'s recommended to check with the specific cruise operator in advance regarding ramps, elevators, and accessible restrooms on board.','Spring and Summer','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"21:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"21:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"21:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"21:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"21:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"21:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"21:00\"}]','Explore Amsterdam\'s iconic canals on a relaxing cruise. Discover the city\'s historic architecture, charming houseboats, and vibrant atmosphere from a unique perspective. A must-do for any visitor to Amsterdam.',60,'[\"Admire the picturesque canal houses with their gabled facades.\", \"Cruise past the iconic Anne Frank House.\", \"See the Skinny Bridge (Magere Brug), Amsterdam\'s most famous bridge.\", \"Learn about the city\'s history and culture from the onboard commentary.\", \"Enjoy stunning views of the Westerkerk church.\", \"Pass through the Jordaan district, known for its charming streets and independent shops.\", \"Observe the vibrant houseboat community along the canals.\", \"Take in the beauty of the canals illuminated at night (during evening cruises).\"]','2025-12-11 10:32:49','2025-12-11 10:32:49'),(3,3,'{\"email\": {\"url\": null, \"value\": null}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+31205308500\", \"value\": \"+31 20 530 8500\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"https://www.thedungeons.com/amsterdam/nl\", \"value\": \"www.thedungeons.com/amsterdam/nl\"}}','The Amsterdam Dungeon has limited accessibility due to the historical nature of the building. Unfortunately, wheelchair access is not available for the entire experience as it involves stairs. Contact the attraction directly for specific details and assistance.','Spring and Summer','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"11:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"11:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"11:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"11:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"11:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"11:00\", \"close_time\": \"19:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"11:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}]','Experience Amsterdam\'s dark history through thrilling live-actor shows. The Amsterdam Dungeon takes you on a journey through 500 years of horrifying events. Prepare to laugh and scream as you encounter plague victims, torturers, and other terrifying characters.',80,'[\"Witness the horrors of the plague and its gruesome effects.\", \"Experience the terror of the Spanish Inquisition.\", \"Come face to face with Rembrandt as he struggles with his debts.\", \"Encounter the infamous torturer of the VOC, the Dutch East India Company.\", \"Navigate the dark and winding labyrinth, hoping to escape.\", \"Get a taste of what life was like on the Batavia shipwreck.\", \"Judge the crimes of the Witte Wieven (White Women) and their supposed witchcraft.\", \"Survive the chilling courtroom experience.\"]','2025-12-11 10:32:55','2025-12-11 10:32:55'),(4,4,'{\"email\": {\"url\": null, \"value\": null}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+441312252424\", \"value\": \"+44 131 225 2424\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"https://edinburgh.org/\", \"value\": \"www.edinburgh.org\"}}','Accessibility varies widely throughout the Old Town due to its historic nature and cobbled streets. While some attractions offer wheelchair access and elevators, many areas present challenges for those with mobility issues. Accessible restrooms are available at some attractions; inquire in advance.','May to September','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}]','Edinburgh\'s Old Town, a UNESCO World Heritage site, is a captivating maze of narrow streets and historic buildings. Explore its rich history, vibrant culture, and iconic landmarks. This is the heart of Edinburgh\'s story.',240,'[\"Explore Edinburgh Castle, perched atop an extinct volcano.\", \"Walk the Royal Mile, connecting Edinburgh Castle and Holyrood Palace.\", \"Visit St. Giles\' Cathedral, a stunning example of Scottish Gothic architecture.\", \"Descend into Mary King\'s Close, a network of preserved 17th-century streets.\", \"Climb Arthur\'s Seat for panoramic views of the city.\", \"Wander through the Grassmarket, a historic marketplace and site of public executions.\", \"Discover the Scottish National Gallery and its impressive art collection.\", \"Enjoy a traditional Scottish pub experience with live music.\"]','2025-12-11 10:33:02','2025-12-11 10:33:02'),(5,5,'{\"email\": {\"url\": \"mailto:enquiries@rct.uk\", \"value\": \"enquiries@rct.uk\"}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+443031237306\", \"value\": \"+44 303 123 7306\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"https://www.rct.uk/visit/palace-of-holyroodhouse\", \"value\": \"www.rct.uk/visit/palace-of-holyroodhouse\"}}','Holyrood Palace offers good accessibility for visitors with disabilities. Wheelchair access is available throughout most of the Palace, and there are lifts to all floors. Accessible restrooms are also available on site.','Spring/Summer','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"16:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": true, \"open_time\": null, \"close_time\": null}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": true, \"open_time\": null, \"close_time\": null}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"16:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"16:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"16:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"16:30\"}]','The Palace of Holyroodhouse, the Queen\'s official residence in Scotland, stands at the end of the Royal Mile. Explore the Palace\'s rich history, from its origins as an abbey to its royal connections. Discover the State Apartments, the historic chambers of Mary, Queen of Scots, and the ruins of Holyrood Abbey.',150,'[\"Tour the State Apartments, reflecting changing tastes of successive monarchs.\", \"See the chambers of Mary, Queen of Scots, including the site of the murder of David Rizzio.\", \"Explore the ruins of Holyrood Abbey, a testament to Scotland\'s monastic past.\", \"Walk through the Royal Gardens and enjoy the serene landscape.\", \"View the Great Gallery, adorned with portraits of Scottish monarchs.\", \"Discover the Throne Room, where investitures and state occasions are held.\", \"Learn about the history of the Palace through informative exhibits and audio guides.\", \"Visit the Queen\'s Gallery, showcasing rotating exhibitions from the Royal Collection.\"]','2025-12-11 10:33:08','2025-12-11 10:33:08'),(6,6,'{\"email\": {\"url\": \"mailto:enquiries@realmarykingsclose.com\", \"value\": \"enquiries@realmarykingsclose.com\"}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+441312250672\", \"value\": \"+44 131 225 0672\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"https://realmarykingsclose.com/\", \"value\": \"realmarykingsclose.com\"}}','Unfortunately, due to the historic nature of the close, wheelchair access is extremely limited. There are steep staircases and uneven surfaces throughout the tour. The entrance and shop are accessible.','Spring and Fall offer pleasant weather and fewer crowds compared to the summer months. Winter can be atmospheric but also cold.','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"21:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"21:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"21:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"21:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"21:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"21:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"21:00\"}]','Descend beneath the Royal Mile to explore the preserved 17th-century streets of Mary King\'s Close. Discover stories of plague victims and the everyday lives of Edinburgh residents. Experience a unique and atmospheric journey through history.',60,'[\"Explore the narrow and winding underground streets\", \"Hear the chilling tales of the Close\'s former residents\", \"Learn about the plague and its impact on Edinburgh\", \"Visit the memorial room dedicated to Annie, the lost child\", \"See the preserved rooms and artifacts from the 17th century\", \"Experience the atmospheric lighting and sound effects\", \"Discover the hidden history beneath the Royal Mile\", \"Take guided tour led by costumed character\"]','2025-12-11 10:33:15','2025-12-11 10:33:15'),(7,7,'{\"email\": {\"url\": \"mailto:info@themobmuseum.org\", \"value\": \"info@themobmuseum.org\"}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+17022292734\", \"value\": \"+1 702-229-2734\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"https://themobmuseum.org/\", \"value\": \"themobmuseum.org\"}}','The Mob Museum is wheelchair accessible, with elevators available to access all floors. Accessible restrooms are located throughout the museum, ensuring a comfortable experience for all visitors.','Fall','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"21:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"21:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"21:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"21:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"21:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"21:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"21:00\"}]','The Mob Museum in Las Vegas offers a gripping and auth