day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"11:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"11:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"11:00\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"11:00\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}]','Zoo Aquarium Madrid is a zoological park in Madrid, Spain, housing a diverse collection of animals from around the world. It\'s a popular attraction for families and animal lovers. The aquarium houses a wide array of marine life.',240,'[\"Giant Pandas: Observe these endangered animals in their habitat.\", \"Dolphin Show: Enjoy an entertaining and educational dolphin show.\", \"Aquarium: Explore the diverse marine life in the aquarium.\", \"Birds of Prey Show: Witness the impressive flight skills of birds of prey.\", \"Gorilla Exhibit: See the Western Lowland gorillas in a naturalistic environment.\", \"Tiger and Lion Exhibits: Marvel at these majestic big cats.\", \"Penguin Area: Watch the penguins swim and play.\", \"Reptile House: Discover various reptiles and amphibians from around the globe.\"]','2025-12-11 10:33:40','2025-12-11 10:33:40'),(11,11,'{\"email\": {\"url\": \"mailto:info@eurekaskydeck.com.au\", \"value\": \"info@eurekaskydeck.com.au\"}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+61396938888\", \"value\": \"+61 3 9693 8888\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"https://www.melbourneskydeck.com.au/\", \"value\": \"www.melbourneskydeck.com.au\"}}','Eureka Skydeck is wheelchair accessible, with elevators providing access to all levels. Accessible restrooms are available. Ramps and other features are in place to ensure a comfortable visit for guests with mobility impairments.','Spring (September-November) or Autumn (March-May) offer pleasant weather and fewer crowds than the peak summer months.','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"12:00\", \"close_time\": \"22:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"12:00\", \"close_time\": \"22:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"12:00\", \"close_time\": \"22:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"12:00\", \"close_time\": \"22:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"12:00\", \"close_time\": \"22:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"12:00\", \"close_time\": \"22:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"12:00\", \"close_time\": \"22:00\"}]','Eureka Skydeck 88 offers unparalleled 360-degree views of Melbourne and beyond. Located on the 88th floor of the Eureka Tower, it\'s the highest public vantage point in the Southern Hemisphere. Experience the thrill of \'The Edge\', a glass cube extending from the building.',90,'[\"Breathtaking 360-degree panoramic views of Melbourne, Port Phillip Bay, and the Dandenong Ranges.\", \"The Edge: A thrilling glass cube that projects 3 meters out from the building, offering a unique perspective.\", \"Floor 88 Viewing Platform: Enjoy the incredible views from the highest vantage point in the Southern Hemisphere.\", \"Viewfinders: Interactive displays that provide information about Melbourne\'s landmarks and history.\", \"Eureka 89 Dining Experience: Indulge in fine dining with spectacular views from the restaurant on level 89 (separate booking required).\", \"Photograph Melbourne: Capture stunning photos of the city skyline at different times of day.\", \"Learn about Melbourne: Discover facts and history about the city\'s landmarks through interactive displays.\", \"Souvenir Shop: Browse a wide selection of souvenirs and gifts to remember your visit.\"]','2025-12-11 10:33:47','2025-12-11 10:33:47'),(12,12,'{\"email\": {\"url\": \"mailto:melbourneaquarium@merlinentertainments.com.au\", \"value\": \"melbourneaquarium@merlinentertainments.com.au\"}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+61399235999\", \"value\": \"+61 3 9923 5999\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"https://www.visitsealife.com/melbourne/?utm_source=gmb&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=yext&utm_content=2\", \"value\": \"www.visitsealife.com/melbourne/?utm_source=gmb&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=yext&utm_content=2\"}}','Melbourne Aquarium offers wheelchair access throughout the attraction. Lifts are available to all levels, and accessible restrooms are conveniently located. The aquarium strives to provide a comfortable and inclusive experience for all visitors.','Spring and Autumn offer pleasant weather and fewer crowds, making them ideal times to visit.','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}]','Explore the underwater wonders of SEA LIFE Melbourne Aquarium. Discover thousands of marine creatures from around the world. Experience interactive exhibits and get up close with fascinating wildlife.',120,'[\"Marvel at the King and Gentoo Penguins in their icy habitat.\", \"Walk through the glass tunnel of the Oceanarium surrounded by sharks and rays.\", \"Discover colourful coral reefs and tropical fish in the Coral Atoll exhibit.\", \"Encounter rescued sea turtles at the Turtle Rehab Centre.\", \"Get hands-on with marine invertebrates in the Rockpools.\", \"See majestic sharks in the Shipwreck Explorer exhibit.\", \"Learn about the aquarium\'s conservation efforts.\", \"Attend an informative talk or feeding session with the marine experts.\"]','2025-12-11 10:33:53','2025-12-11 10:33:53'),(13,13,'{\"email\": {\"url\": \"mailto:zoodesk@zoo.org.au\", \"value\": \"zoodesk@zoo.org.au\"}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+611300966784\", \"value\": \"+61 1300 966 784\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"https://www.zoo.org.au/melbourne\", \"value\": \"www.zoo.org.au/melbourne\"}}','Melbourne Zoo offers excellent accessibility with wheelchair access throughout the grounds, including ramps and elevators where needed. Accessible restrooms are conveniently located, and wheelchairs are available for hire.','Spring and Autumn offer pleasant weather and fewer crowds, making for an ideal visit.','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}]','Melbourne Zoo is home to over 3000 animals from around the world. As Victoria\'s oldest zoo, it plays a vital role in conservation and education. Explore diverse habitats and encounter fascinating wildlife.',240,'[\"See the Orangutans in their amazing treetop habitat.\", \"Visit the playful penguins at the Penguin Precinct.\", \"Explore the Trail of Elephants and learn about their conservation.\", \"Discover the diverse array of native Australian animals.\", \"Wander through the Butterfly House and admire the colourful butterflies.\", \"Attend a Keeper Talk to learn more about your favourite animals.\", \"Enjoy a picnic in the beautiful gardens.\", \"Explore the Lemur Lookout\"]','2025-12-11 10:33:59','2025-12-11 10:33:59'),(14,14,'{\"email\": {\"url\": \"mailto:info@jungleisland.com\", \"value\": \"info@jungleisland.com\"}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+13054007000\", \"value\": \"+1 305-400-7000\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"https://www.jungleisland.com/\", \"value\": \"www.jungleisland.com\"}}','Jungle Island strives to be accessible to all guests. The park offers wheelchair rentals and accessible restrooms. While some areas may have limited accessibility due to the natural terrain, most exhibits and shows are designed to accommodate wheelchairs and other mobility devices.','Winter/Spring','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"16:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"16:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"16:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"16:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"16:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"16:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"16:00\"}]','Jungle Island is an interactive zoological park located in Miami, Florida. It\'s renowned for its diverse collection of animals, engaging shows, and immersive jungle-like environment. Visitors can experience up-close encounters with exotic birds, mammals, and reptiles.',240,'[\"Meet the colorful and talkative parrots in the Parrot Bowl.\", \"Observe the majestic cassowary, one of the world\'s most dangerous birds.\", \"Experience the thrilling Winged Wonders show featuring free-flying birds.\", \"Get up close with sloths and other fascinating creatures.\", \"Explore the Manu Wildlife Center and learn about South American wildlife.\", \"Take photos with the friendly macaws.\", \"Enjoy the lush landscaping and jungle atmosphere.\", \"Learn about conservation efforts and animal welfare.\"]','2025-12-11 10:34:06','2025-12-11 10:34:06'),(15,15,'{\"email\": {\"url\": \"mailto:info@junglequeen.com\", \"value\": \"info@junglequeen.com\"}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+19544625596\", \"value\": \"+1 954-462-5596\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"http://www.junglequeen.com/\", \"value\": \"www.junglequeen.com\"}}','The Jungle Queen Riverboat offers limited wheelchair accessibility. Please contact them directly to confirm specific accessibility needs and accommodations for boarding and navigating the boat and related facilities. The Bahia Mar Yachting Center is mostly accessible.','Winter (December - February)','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"18:00\"}]','The Jungle Queen Riverboat is a Fort Lauderdale icon, offering narrated sightseeing cruises along the New River. Experience the Millionaire\'s Row of lavish homes and yachts. Enjoy dinner and a show on a tropical isle.',180,'[\"Narrated sightseeing cruise along the New River.\", \"Views of Millionaire\'s Row and impressive yachts.\", \"Tropical Isle Dinner Cruise with live entertainment.\", \"Jungle Queen\'s Tropical Village with exotic birds and animals (on Dinner Cruise).\", \"The lively and entertaining show on the Dinner Cruise.\", \"Opportunity to see celebrity homes from the water.\", \"Sunset views over the Intracoastal Waterway (on select cruises).\", \"The historical aspect of cruising on a classic riverboat.\"]','2025-12-11 10:34:12','2025-12-11 10:34:12'),(16,16,'{\"email\": {\"url\": \"mailto:info@lioncountrysafari.com\", \"value\": \"info@lioncountrysafari.com\"}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+15617931084\", \"value\": \"+1 561-793-1084\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"http://www.lioncountrysafari.com/\", \"value\": \"www.lioncountrysafari.com\"}}','Lion Country Safari offers wheelchair accessibility throughout the drive-through safari and the amusement park. Accessible restrooms and designated parking spaces are available. Certain rides may have specific restrictions; please check with park staff for details.','Winter (November - April)','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:30\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}]','Lion Country Safari is a unique drive-through safari and amusement park. Experience hundreds of animals roaming freely in naturalistic habitats. Enjoy rides, animal shows, and water play in the adjacent park.',300,'[\"Drive through the seven distinct sections of the safari, observing lions, giraffes, zebras, and more.\", \"Visit the giraffe feeding exhibit for an up-close encounter.\", \"Enjoy the water park with slides and interactive water features (seasonal).\", \"Ride the carousel, Ferris wheel, or other amusement park rides.\", \"Attend an animal encounter show to learn about the park\'s residents.\", \"Explore the petting zoo and interact with domestic animals.\", \"Have lunch at the park\'s restaurant or cafe.\", \"Browse the gift shop for souvenirs of your safari adventure.\"]','2025-12-11 10:34:18','2025-12-11 10:34:18'),(17,17,'{\"email\": {\"url\": \"mailto:accueil.catacombes@paris.fr\", \"value\": \"accueil.catacombes@paris.fr\"}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+33143224763\", \"value\": \"+33 1 43 22 47 63\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"https://www.catacombes.paris.fr/\", \"value\": \"www.catacombes.paris.fr\"}}','The Catacombs are unfortunately not wheelchair accessible due to the presence of numerous stairs and narrow passages. There are no elevators available. The site is generally not recommended for individuals with mobility issues.','Spring and Fall are the best times to visit to avoid the extreme heat and crowds of summer.','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": true, \"open_time\": \"09:45\", \"close_time\": \"20:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:45\", \"close_time\": \"20:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:45\", \"close_time\": \"20:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:45\", \"close_time\": \"20:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:45\", \"close_time\": \"20:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:45\", \"close_time\": \"20:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:45\", \"close_time\": \"20:30\"}]','The Catacombs of Paris are an underground ossuary holding the remains of more than six million people. Created in the late 18th century to relieve overcrowded cemeteries, they offer a chilling glimpse into Parisian history. Descend to explore this unique and unforgettable subterranean world.',60,'[\"The Descent: Experience the spiral staircase descent into the depths.\", \"The Ossuary: Walk through the corridors lined with meticulously arranged skulls and bones.\", \"The Quarrymen\'s Foot Bath: Discover a naturally formed pool used by quarry workers.\", \"The Sacellum (Chapel): Admire a small altar constructed within the ossuary.\", \"The Poem Inscriptions: Read the verses and philosophical quotes inscribed on the walls.\", \"The Fountain of Samuel: See a fountain that quarry workers used to measure the volume of the limestone they were excavating.\", \"The History Panels: Learn about the origins and history of the Catacombs through informative displays.\", \"The atmosphere of the underground tunnels\"]','2025-12-11 10:34:24','2025-12-11 10:34:24'),(18,18,'{\"email\": {\"url\": null, \"value\": null}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+33144752000\", \"value\": \"+33 1 44 75 20 00\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"http://www.parczoologiquedeparis.fr/\", \"value\": \"www.parczoologiquedeparis.fr\"}}','The Paris Zoological Park is mostly wheelchair accessible, with adapted routes throughout the different biozones. Elevators are available in some pavilions to access different levels. Accessible restrooms are also available.','Spring and Summer','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"10:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:00\"}]','The Paris Zoological Park, also known as the Vincennes Zoo, offers a fascinating journey through five biozones: Patagonia, Sahel-Sudan, Europe, Guyana, and Madagascar. Discover diverse ecosystems and iconic species in this immersive wildlife experience. It\'s a great place to learn about biodiversity and conservation efforts.',240,'[\"The Great Aviary in the Guyana zone, home to diverse bird species.\", \"The Manatees in the Guyana area.\", \"The European zone, showcasing local wildlife like wolves and lynx.\", \"The iconic Great Rock, offering panoramic views of the zoo.\", \"The Sahel-Sudan zone, featuring giraffes, lions, and other African animals.\", \"The Madagascar zone, with its lemurs and unique flora.\", \"The Penguin and Sea Lion shows (check schedule upon arrival).\", \"Interactive exhibits and educational programs for children.\"]','2025-12-11 10:34:31','2025-12-11 10:34:31'),(19,19,'{\"email\": {\"url\": \"mailto:null\", \"value\": \"null\"}, \"phone\": {\"url\": \"tel:+33155258210\", \"value\": \"+33 1 55 25 82 10\"}, \"website\": {\"url\": \"https://www.paris.fr/dossiers/bienvenue-au-cimetiere-du-pere-lachaise-47/\", \"value\": \"www.paris.fr/dossiers/bienvenue-au-cimetiere-du-pere-lachaise-47\"}}','The cemetery has uneven surfaces and numerous stairs, making wheelchair access challenging in some areas. Certain sections are more accessible than others, but generally, full accessibility is limited. There are accessible restrooms available near the main entrance.','Spring and Fall (April-May & September-October)','[{\"day\": \"Monday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"08:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Tuesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"08:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Wednesday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"08:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Thursday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"08:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Friday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"08:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Saturday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"08:30\", \"close_time\": \"17:30\"}, {\"day\": \"Sunday\", \"is_closed\": false, \"open_time\": \"09:00\", \"close_time\": \"17:30\"}]','Père Lachaise Cemetery is the largest cemetery in Paris and one of the most famous in the world. It\'s a beautiful and serene final resting place for many notable figures in history. Explore its winding paths and discover stunning monuments and sculptures.',120,'[\"Visit the tomb of Jim Morrison, lead singer of The Doors.\", \"Pay respects at the grave of Oscar Wilde, covered in lipstick kisses.\", \"Admire the touching monument to Victor Noir, a journalist whose tomb is said to bring fertility.\", \"Find the graves of Édith Piaf, a legendary French singer.\", \"Discover the final resting place of Frédéric Chopin, the famous composer.\", \"Explore the art and architecture of the various tombs and monuments.\", \"Wander through the peaceful, tree-lined paths and reflect on history.\", \"Seek out the grave of Marcel Proust, author of \'In Search of Lost Time.\'\"]','2025-12-11 10:34:37','2025-12-11 10:34:37');
