INSERT INTO `attractions` VALUES (1,1,'amaze-amsterdam','Amaze Amsterdam','ChIJ2xlnX77jxUcR2WgrWg7Ehxk',4.60,7154,'Visitors rave about AMAZE Amsterdam\'s immersive and unique experience, describing it as an interactive light and laser show with amazing sound and music. The friendly and helpful staff also contribute significantly to the positive atmosphere, making it a memorable activity for various age groups.',52.393968,4.851477,'2025-12-11 05:02:29','2025-12-11 10:33:07'),(2,1,'amsterdam-canal-cruise','Amsterdam Canal Cruise','ChIJIaP3F-0JxkcRsjmw80fNMrA',4.40,2191,'Amsterdam canal cruises are a must-do for first-time visitors, offering a relaxing and scenic way to see the city\'s iconic landmarks and learn about its history. Visitors appreciate the comfortable boats, informative audio guides, and unique perspective of Amsterdam from the waterways. Whether it\'s a sunny day or even in winter with covered and heated boats, it\'s a great experience.',52.378676,4.897165,'2025-12-11 05:02:29','2025-12-11 10:33:45'),(3,1,'amsterdam-dungeon','Amsterdam Dungeon','ChIJC7Uw48AJxkcR28umcgx0C6k',4.50,13680,'Visitors rave about the Amsterdam Dungeon\'s immersive and engaging experience, highlighting the talented actors and a perfect blend of humor, horror, and interactive storytelling. Many reviewers also appreciate the value for the price and the memorable moments created within the dungeon\'s atmosphere.',52.370198,4.892168,'2025-12-11 05:02:29','2025-12-11 10:33:59'),(4,2,'edinburgh-old-town','Edinburgh Old Town','ChIJc1I_X4XHh0gRV9nOqdrZAnk',4.60,125482,'Edinburgh Old Town is a historic gem, drawing visitors in with its charming architecture, cobbled streets, and vibrant atmosphere. The Royal Mile is a must-see, offering a journey through Scottish history and culture. Many recommend taking a guided walking tour to fully appreciate the area\'s rich heritage.',55.951902,-3.190420,'2025-12-11 05:02:29','2025-12-11 10:34:26'),(5,2,'holyrood-palace','Holyrood Palace','ChIJA6CjF3e4h0gR1vlnGdvUqyc',4.60,21680,'Visitors rave about the Palace of Holyroodhouse\'s stunning architecture, informative audio guide, and fascinating insights into Scottish royal history. The beautiful gardens and royal rooms create a memorable and engaging experience, making it a worthwhile stop in Edinburgh. Despite the lack of photography inside, many find the palace well-maintained and suitable for all ages.',55.952695,-3.171613,'2025-12-11 05:02:29','2025-12-11 10:34:33'),(6,2,'mary-king-s-close','Mary King’s Close','ChIJyVmEW4XHh0gRiXVkzxH0ZMs',4.60,16386,'Visitors rave about the fascinating history and unique experience of walking through the underground close. The engaging and knowledgeable tour guides, often in character, are consistently highlighted as making the tour exceptional and a must-do in Edinburgh.',55.950234,-3.190555,'2025-12-11 05:02:29','2025-12-11 10:34:46'),(7,3,'mob-museum','Mob Museum','ChIJ6dSwgwrDyIARnTLnwBzbNVU',4.60,19079,'Visitors rave about the Mob Museum\'s immersive and informative exhibits, appreciating the authentic portrayal of both sides of organized crime. Interactive experiences like the shooting simulator and distillery are also big hits, providing engaging entertainment. The museum offers a fascinating and memorable Vegas experience beyond the casinos.',36.172484,-115.141577,'2025-12-11 05:02:29','2025-12-11 10:35:00'),(8,3,'natural-history-museum','Natural History Museum','ChIJEYSZ3w7DyIARfTw1yvRJL9A',4.50,1563,'Visitors rave about the museum\'s diverse and engaging exhibits, from animatronic dinosaurs to Egyptian artifacts. It\'s a hit with families, especially grandparents and grandkids, and even adults enjoy exploring the informative displays and recent upgrades. The friendly staff and well-priced tickets add to the positive experience.',51.496511,-0.176002,'2025-12-11 05:02:29','2025-12-11 10:35:13'),(9,3,'neue-nationalgalerie','Neue Nationalgalerie','ChIJB0lB0RNRqEcRqEqMbRQEfq4',3.10,48,'Visitors appreciate the café\'s convenient location within the gallery and its unique atmosphere, highlighted by beautiful walls and lamps. While service experiences can vary, many enjoy the coffee and find the staff friendly.',52.507041,13.367621,'2025-12-11 05:02:29','2025-12-11 10:35:26'),(10,4,'zoo-aquarium-madrid','Zoo Aquarium Madrid','ChIJHQS2xgqIQQ0RgyGlQ3AakYk',4.20,39683,'Visitors love the Zoo Aquarium de Madrid for its well-maintained habitats, diverse animal selection, and relaxed atmosphere. It\'s considered a perfect family outing with engaging exhibits, especially for children, making it a highly recommended experience.',40.409149,-3.761069,'2025-12-11 05:02:29','2025-12-11 10:35:39'),(11,5,'eureka-skydeck','Eureka Skydeck','ChIJQffkhK1C1moR3Z0-w-t8SS8',4.50,16862,'Visitors rave about the Melbourne Skydeck\'s stunning panoramic views of the city, especially at sunset. The experience is praised for being well-organized, family-friendly, and a must-do for first-time visitors, offering drinks and snacks to enjoy while taking in the scenery.',-37.821691,144.964525,'2025-12-11 05:02:29','2025-12-11 10:35:53'),(12,5,'melbourne-aquarium','Melbourne Aquarium','ChIJ_QzhcE1d1moR9rtoKagNPOI',4.30,18417,'Visitors love the diverse exhibits, especially the jellyfish and interactive rockpool, making it an enjoyable experience for all ages. Many appreciate the helpful staff and the chance to learn about marine life. It\'s a worthwhile family activity, though some find it can get crowded.',-38.045016,145.353057,'2025-12-11 05:02:29','2025-12-11 10:36:06'),(13,5,'melbourne-zoo','Melbourne Zoo','ChIJl4pG29Bc1moRisNvMITeH7Y',4.30,6391,'Visitors love the Melbourne Zoo for its great variety of animals and well-maintained habitats. Many highlight favorite exhibits like the lemurs and meerkats, and appreciate the zoo\'s educational focus and conservation efforts. It\'s often described as a fun day out for the whole family.',-37.784803,144.951537,'2025-12-11 05:02:29','2025-12-11 10:36:19'),(14,6,'jungle-island','Jungle Island','ChIJkWXRuBC02YgRripCIoUAN9g',4.10,6182,'Visitors love the beautiful and colorful light displays, especially during Luminosa, which offers unique experiences each year. Interacting with the animals, particularly the lemurs, is also a highlight. However, the separate and expensive parking fee is a common concern.',25.786178,-80.174694,'2025-12-11 05:02:29','2025-12-11 10:36:31'),(15,6,'jungle-queen','Jungle Queen','ChIJq81qhSUA2YgReR6zm924wNI',4.50,5884,'Visitors love the Jungle Queen Riverboat for its scenic views of impressive yachts and homes, as well as the lively Polynesian show on the island.  Many appreciate the engaging tour guides and find the overall experience fun and memorable, especially when purchased at a discount.',53.387366,-131.932225,'2025-12-11 05:02:29','2025-12-11 10:37:01'),(16,6,'lion-country-safari','Lion Country Safari','ChIJJYiDRgcx2YgRWQ9Vze8pUXk',4.60,14065,'Visitors rave about the amazing experience of driving through the safari, seeing a diverse array of animals in natural habitats with a helpful audio guide. The park also offers a walk-through area with more animals, a boat tour, and attractions for kids, making it a fun-filled day for all ages.',26.713773,-80.322078,'2025-12-11 05:02:29','2025-12-11 10:37:15'),(17,7,'paris-catacombs','Paris Catacombs','ChIJdbbQwbZx5kcRs7Qu5nPw18g',4.00,10230,'Visitors love the unique and immersive experience of walking through the Catacombs\' fascinating labyrinth of bones. The historical significance, well-organized tours with informative audio guides, and the overall ambiance make it a memorable and humbling must-see attraction in Paris. Booking tickets in advance is highly recommended.',48.833744,2.332293,'2025-12-11 05:02:29','2025-12-11 10:37:41'),(18,7,'paris-zoo','Paris Zoo','ChIJgxOy6vRy5kcRuuupiLDdw3A',4.30,18642,'Visitors love the Parc zoologique de Paris for its diverse animal collection, spacious and well-maintained enclosures that prioritize animal welfare. Highlights include the immersive bird aviary, tropical greenhouse, and innovative savanna area.',48.831884,2.418395,'2025-12-11 05:02:29','2025-12-11 10:37:55'),(19,7,'p-re-lachaise-cemetery','Père Lachaise Cemetery','ChIJhadpXItt5kcRGWQLUydhz6E',4.60,4340,'Visitors love Père-Lachaise for its historical and artistic atmosphere, finding it easy to spend hours exploring the elaborate tombstones and the stories they tell. Many appreciate the opportunity to connect with notable figures and find inspiration within the cemetery\'s grounds. It\'s a unique and reflective experience, best enjoyed with a map and plenty of time.',48.861130,2.394009,'2025-12-11 05:02:29','2025-12-11 10:38:12');
