INSERT INTO `tips` VALUES (1,2,'SAFETY','Be vigilant against pickpockets, especially in crowded boarding areas and on popular routes.','Gemini (Amsterdam Canal Cruise)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:33:43'),(2,2,'SAFETY','Board and disembark carefully. The boats often rock slightly, and the steps can be slippery, especially in wet weather. Pay attention to the crew\'s instructions.','Gemini (Amsterdam Canal Cruise)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:33:43'),(3,2,'SAFETY','Keep a close eye on your belongings, particularly cameras and phones, especially when taking photos near the water\'s edge. Secure them with a strap or keep them in a zipped bag.','Gemini (Amsterdam Canal Cruise)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:33:43'),(4,2,'SAFETY','Stay seated while the boat is in motion. Standing can be dangerous due to sudden stops or waves, especially if you\'re near the edge of the boat.','Gemini (Amsterdam Canal Cruise)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:33:43'),(5,2,'INSIDER','Book your canal cruise online in advance to secure your spot and often get a better price.','Gemini (Amsterdam Canal Cruise)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:33:43'),(6,2,'INSIDER','Take a cruise during the Amsterdam Light Festival (winter) for a magical illuminated experience.','Gemini (Amsterdam Canal Cruise)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:33:43'),(7,2,'INSIDER','Opt for a smaller, open-boat canal cruise for a more intimate and less crowded experience. These boats can often navigate smaller canals that larger boats can\'t access.','Gemini (Amsterdam Canal Cruise)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:33:43'),(8,2,'INSIDER','Consider taking a late afternoon or early evening cruise for stunning golden hour lighting, perfect for photos of the canals and historic buildings. This is a popular time, so book ahead.','Gemini (Amsterdam Canal Cruise)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:33:43'),(9,2,'INSIDER','Look for canal cruises that include live commentary from local guides for a more engaging and informative experience. They often share interesting stories and insights about the city\'s history and culture.','Gemini (Amsterdam Canal Cruise)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:33:43'),(10,2,'INSIDER','Bring your own drinks and snacks to save money, as onboard options can be expensive. Just be mindful of keeping the boat clean and tidy.','Gemini (Amsterdam Canal Cruise)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:33:43'),(11,2,'INSIDER','If you\'re visiting during peak season, try to take a cruise outside of the main tourist hours (mid-morning to late afternoon) to avoid the biggest crowds. Early morning cruises can be especially peaceful.','Gemini (Amsterdam Canal Cruise)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:33:43'),(12,4,'SAFETY','Be aware of your belongings, especially in crowded areas like the Royal Mile, as pickpockets operate in these tourist hotspots.','Gemini (Edinburgh Old Town)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:34:18'),(13,4,'SAFETY','The Royal Mile can get extremely congested, particularly during the Edinburgh Fringe Festival and peak tourist season. Stay aware of your surroundings and avoid getting separated from your group.','Gemini (Edinburgh Old Town)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:34:18'),(14,4,'SAFETY','Cobblestone streets and uneven pavements are prevalent throughout the Old Town. Wear comfortable, sturdy shoes and watch your step to avoid trips and falls.','Gemini (Edinburgh Old Town)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:34:18'),(15,4,'INSIDER','Escape the Royal Mile crowds by exploring the charming Cockburn Street, with its unique shops and cafes.','Gemini (Edinburgh Old Town)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:34:18'),(16,4,'INSIDER','For stunning photo opportunities, head to Victoria Street (said to be the inspiration for Diagon Alley in Harry Potter) early in the morning before the shops open and the crowds arrive.','Gemini (Edinburgh Old Town)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:34:18'),(17,4,'INSIDER','Enjoy a traditional Scottish pub meal at lunchtime for lower prices than dinner. Many pubs offer lunch specials that are great value for money.','Gemini (Edinburgh Old Town)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:34:18'),(18,5,'SAFETY','Stay on marked paths, particularly when exploring the Abbey ruins and gardens. Uneven ground and crumbling stonework can be hazardous, especially in wet weather.','Gemini (Holyrood Palace)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:34:31'),(19,5,'SAFETY','Wear comfortable shoes suitable for walking on cobblestones and potentially slippery surfaces, especially if visiting after rain. The grounds are extensive and require walking.','Gemini (Holyrood Palace)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:34:31'),(20,5,'SAFETY','If you have any mobility issues, check the accessibility information in advance. Some areas of the Palace have limited access; plan your visit accordingly.','Gemini (Holyrood Palace)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:34:31'),(21,5,'INSIDER','Check the official website for closure dates due to Royal events; you don\'t want to miss out!','Gemini (Holyrood Palace)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:34:31'),(22,5,'INSIDER','Take your time in the Great Gallery; look closely at the portraits of the Scottish monarchs and try to spot the hidden stories and details within them. It\'s easy to rush through, but well worth lingering.','Gemini (Holyrood Palace)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:34:31'),(23,5,'INSIDER','Walk through the Abbey ruins at the back of the palace. Many people skip it, but it\'s a truly atmospheric and beautiful spot, particularly on a clear day. It provides a great view of Arthur\'s Seat.','Gemini (Holyrood Palace)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:34:31'),(24,5,'INSIDER','Budget extra time to explore the Queen\'s Gallery, if it\'s open. It often hosts fascinating exhibitions of items from the Royal Collection which complements the palace tour well. It requires a separate ticket.','Gemini (Holyrood Palace)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:34:31'),(25,5,'INSIDER','Look for the tiny details! The palace is full of historical quirks like the original floor tiles in Mary Queen of Scots\' chambers and hidden symbols in the plasterwork.','Gemini (Holyrood Palace)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:34:31'),(26,5,'INSIDER','Consider purchasing a Royal Collection Trust membership if you plan to visit multiple Royal residences during your trip; it can offer significant savings on admission fees.','Gemini (Holyrood Palace)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:34:31'),(27,7,'SAFETY','Be aware of your surroundings, especially in crowded areas, as pickpockets can operate in tourist hotspots.','Gemini (Mob Museum)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:34:59'),(28,7,'SAFETY','Keep your belongings secure and within sight at all times. Consider using a crossbody bag or a money belt to deter theft, particularly in crowded exhibits.','Gemini (Mob Museum)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:34:59'),(29,7,'SAFETY','Stay hydrated, especially during the hotter months. The museum can get crowded, and staying hydrated will help you avoid feeling lightheaded or unwell. Water is available for purchase inside.','Gemini (Mob Museum)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:34:59'),(30,7,'SAFETY','If you have mobility concerns, check the museum\'s website or inquire at the front desk about accessibility options, including wheelchair rentals and elevator access. Plan your route in advance.','Gemini (Mob Museum)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:34:59'),(31,7,'INSIDER','Visit during off-peak hours (weekdays, mornings) for smaller crowds and a more immersive experience.','Gemini (Mob Museum)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:34:59'),(32,7,'INSIDER','Don\'t miss the basement speakeasy – it offers a unique atmosphere and themed cocktails!','Gemini (Mob Museum)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:34:59'),(33,7,'INSIDER','Purchase tickets online in advance to skip the ticket line, especially during peak season. This can save you a significant amount of time and allow you to start exploring sooner.','Gemini (Mob Museum)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:34:59'),(34,7,'INSIDER','Take advantage of the interactive exhibits, such as the firearms training simulator (additional cost). They offer a hands-on learning experience that enhances the visit.','Gemini (Mob Museum)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:34:59'),(35,7,'INSIDER','Look for the original courtroom where the Kefauver hearings took place. It\'s a powerful and historically significant space within the museum, often overlooked by casual visitors.','Gemini (Mob Museum)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:34:59'),(36,7,'INSIDER','Factor in at least 3-4 hours for your visit to fully explore all three floors of exhibits. There\'s a lot of information to absorb, and you don\'t want to feel rushed.','Gemini (Mob Museum)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:34:59'),(37,7,'INSIDER','Check the Mob Museum\'s website for special events, lectures, and tours that might coincide with your visit. These can provide deeper insights into specific topics and personalities.','Gemini (Mob Museum)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:34:59'),(38,8,'SAFETY','Be aware of your surroundings, especially in crowded areas. Keep valuables secure to prevent pickpocketing.','Gemini (Natural History Museum)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:35:11'),(39,8,'SAFETY','Stay hydrated, especially during the hotter months. Bring a water bottle and refill it at designated water fountains to avoid dehydration.','Gemini (Natural History Museum)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:35:11'),(40,8,'SAFETY','Supervise children closely at all times, particularly near exhibits with interactive elements. Ensure they understand the rules to prevent accidents or damage.','Gemini (Natural History Museum)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:35:11'),(41,8,'SAFETY','Be mindful of the museum\'s accessibility features and plan your route accordingly. Check the website for details on ramps, elevators, and accessible restrooms.','Gemini (Natural History Museum)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:35:11'),(42,8,'SAFETY','Report any suspicious activity or unattended packages to museum staff immediately. Your vigilance helps maintain a safe environment for everyone.','Gemini (Natural History Museum)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:35:11'),(43,8,'SAFETY','Pay attention to posted signs and warnings, especially regarding restricted areas or hazardous materials. Follow staff instructions at all times.','Gemini (Natural History Museum)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:35:11'),(44,8,'INSIDER','Check the museum\'s website for special events or temporary exhibits before your visit.','Gemini (Natural History Museum)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:35:11'),(45,8,'INSIDER','Allow ample time to explore all exhibits thoroughly. A minimum of 2-3 hours is recommended to appreciate everything the museum has to offer.','Gemini (Natural History Museum)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:35:11'),(46,8,'INSIDER','Don\'t miss the dinosaur exhibit, it\'s a crowd-pleaser! Take your time to read the information panels and appreciate the scale of these prehistoric creatures.','Gemini (Natural History Museum)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:35:11'),(47,8,'INSIDER','Look for the smaller, often overlooked exhibits focusing on local Nevada wildlife. These offer unique insights into the region\'s natural history.','Gemini (Natural History Museum)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:35:11'),(48,8,'INSIDER','Take advantage of the museum\'s educational programs and workshops, especially if traveling with children. These interactive experiences enhance learning and engagement.','Gemini (Natural History Museum)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:35:11'),(58,11,'SAFETY','Be mindful of your belongings in crowded areas, especially near the elevators and viewing platforms, as pickpockets can operate.','Gemini (Eureka Skydeck)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:35:51'),(59,11,'SAFETY','If you have a fear of heights, take it slow and stay away from the edges of the viewing platforms initially. Familiarize yourself with the space before approaching the glass.','Gemini (Eureka Skydeck)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:35:51'),(60,11,'SAFETY','Exercise caution when stepping into and out of \'The Edge\'. Listen carefully to the staff\'s instructions regarding leaning against the glass and ensure you have a firm footing.','Gemini (Eureka Skydeck)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:35:51'),(61,11,'SAFETY','Supervise children closely, especially near the glass windows and elevated areas. Keep them within arm\'s reach to prevent accidents.','Gemini (Eureka Skydeck)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:35:51'),(62,11,'SAFETY','The Skydeck can get very windy at times. Hold onto hats and loose items to prevent them from being blown away, especially when taking photos outside.','Gemini (Eureka Skydeck)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:35:51'),(63,11,'INSIDER','For sunset views and fewer crowds, visit on a weekday evening.','Gemini (Eureka Skydeck)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:35:51'),(64,11,'INSIDER','Check the weather forecast before you go – visibility can be severely limited on cloudy days.','Gemini (Eureka Skydeck)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:35:51'),(65,11,'INSIDER','Head straight to \'The Edge\' upon arrival, as queues can build up quickly. Booking your entry to \'The Edge\' online in advance can also save you time.','Gemini (Eureka Skydeck)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:35:51'),(66,11,'INSIDER','Take advantage of the free telescopes available. They provide enhanced views of specific landmarks and interesting details you might otherwise miss.','Gemini (Eureka Skydeck)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:35:51'),(67,11,'INSIDER','Don\'t miss the interactive displays near the elevators. They provide interesting facts about Melbourne and the construction of Eureka Tower itself, enriching your visit.','Gemini (Eureka Skydeck)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:35:51'),(68,11,'INSIDER','The floor to ceiling windows offer the best photo opportunities. Use natural light to capture the stunning cityscape, especially around sunrise or sunset.','Gemini (Eureka Skydeck)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:35:51'),(69,12,'SAFETY','Be aware of your surroundings and keep a close watch on your belongings, especially in crowded areas like the Oceanarium tunnel, to avoid pickpockets.','Gemini (Melbourne Aquarium)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:05'),(70,12,'SAFETY','Keep a close eye on children at all times, especially near open tanks and interactive exhibits. Ensure they understand not to climb on barriers or tap on the glass.','Gemini (Melbourne Aquarium)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:05'),(71,12,'SAFETY','Be mindful of wet floors, especially around water exhibits and walkways. Wear appropriate footwear with good grip to prevent slips and falls.','Gemini (Melbourne Aquarium)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:05'),(72,12,'SAFETY','Be aware that the lighting inside the aquarium is often dim, which can affect visibility. Allow your eyes to adjust and take extra care when navigating the exhibits to avoid bumping into things.','Gemini (Melbourne Aquarium)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:05'),(73,12,'INSIDER','Check the feeding schedule online beforehand to catch the most exciting presentations.','Gemini (Melbourne Aquarium)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:05'),(74,12,'INSIDER','Head straight to the Oceanarium tunnel upon entry. It\'s usually less crowded at the beginning and end of the day, offering a better viewing experience of the sharks and rays.','Gemini (Melbourne Aquarium)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:05'),(75,12,'INSIDER','Consider purchasing a Melbourne CityPass if you plan to visit other attractions. It often includes entry to the aquarium and can save you money on overall admission costs.','Gemini (Melbourne Aquarium)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:05'),(76,12,'INSIDER','Look for smaller, less-advertised exhibits like the seahorse pier or the rockpool area. These often provide a more intimate and engaging experience with the marine life.','Gemini (Melbourne Aquarium)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:05'),(77,12,'INSIDER','Take advantage of the photo opportunities with the penguin mascots or themed backdrops. These are great for capturing memorable moments of your visit, especially for families with children.','Gemini (Melbourne Aquarium)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:05'),(78,12,'INSIDER','If you\'re interested in marine conservation, ask staff about the aquarium\'s breeding programs and rescue efforts. They can provide insights into the important work being done to protect marine life.','Gemini (Melbourne Aquarium)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:05'),(79,14,'SAFETY','Stay aware of your surroundings, especially during crowded shows, to prevent petty theft. Keep valuables secure.','Gemini (Jungle Island)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:30'),(80,14,'SAFETY','Wear comfortable, closed-toe shoes, as you\'ll be doing a lot of walking on uneven terrain. This minimizes the risk of trips and falls, especially near animal enclosures.','Gemini (Jungle Island)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:30'),(81,14,'SAFETY','Supervise children closely, particularly near animal exhibits and water features. Ensure they follow safety guidelines and maintain a safe distance from the animals to avoid any incidents.','Gemini (Jungle Island)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:30'),(82,14,'INSIDER','Check the show schedule online before your visit and plan your day around the performances you want to see.','Gemini (Jungle Island)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:30'),(83,14,'INSIDER','For the best photos with the parrots, attend the early morning meet-and-greets. The lighting is better and the birds are more active.','Gemini (Jungle Island)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:30'),(84,14,'INSIDER','Take advantage of the interactive animal experiences, but book them in advance. These provide unique opportunities to get up close and personal with the animals.','Gemini (Jungle Island)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:30'),(85,14,'INSIDER','Look for discount tickets online or through partner organizations like AAA. This can significantly reduce the cost of admission.','Gemini (Jungle Island)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:30'),(86,14,'INSIDER','Pack a picnic lunch to save money on food inside the park. There are designated picnic areas where you can enjoy your meal.','Gemini (Jungle Island)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:30'),(87,15,'SAFETY','Be aware of your belongings, especially during boarding and disembarking, as these are crowded times and prime opportunities for petty theft.','Gemini (Jungle Queen)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:59'),(88,15,'SAFETY','Stay hydrated, especially during the day cruises. The Florida sun can be intense, and dehydration can lead to heatstroke. Bring your own water or purchase drinks on board.','Gemini (Jungle Queen)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:59'),(89,15,'SAFETY','Supervise children closely at all times, especially near the railings and on the docks. The water can be dangerous, and a momentary lapse in attention can have serious consequences.','Gemini (Jungle Queen)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:59'),(90,15,'SAFETY','Wear appropriate footwear with good grip, especially if you plan to walk around the island during the stopover. The ground can be uneven and slippery in places.','Gemini (Jungle Queen)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:59'),(91,15,'SAFETY','Be mindful of the sun and apply sunscreen liberally. Even on overcast days, UV rays can penetrate the clouds and cause sunburn. Reapply sunscreen every two hours, or more often if swimming or sweating.','Gemini (Jungle Queen)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:59'),(92,15,'INSIDER','Opt for the evening dinner cruise for a more atmospheric experience with beautiful city lights.','Gemini (Jungle Queen)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:59'),(93,15,'INSIDER','Arrive early to secure a good seat, especially if traveling with a group.','Gemini (Jungle Queen)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:59'),(94,15,'INSIDER','Bring cash for tipping the performers and servers. While card payments may be accepted for tickets and drinks, tips are often preferred in cash. Show your appreciation for their hard work.','Gemini (Jungle Queen)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:59'),(95,15,'INSIDER','Check for online deals and discounts before booking your tickets. Many websites offer promotional codes that can save you money on your Jungle Queen experience.','Gemini (Jungle Queen)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:59'),(96,15,'INSIDER','If you are prone to seasickness, take preventative medication before boarding. The waters can be choppy at times, especially on windy days.','Gemini (Jungle Queen)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:59'),(97,15,'INSIDER','Consider the weather forecast before booking, particularly during hurricane season. While the Jungle Queen operates in various conditions, severe weather can lead to cancellations.','Gemini (Jungle Queen)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:36:59'),(98,18,'SAFETY','Be aware of your belongings, especially in crowded areas like the entrance and popular animal exhibits; pickpockets operate in tourist spots.','Gemini (Paris Zoo)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:37:53'),(99,18,'SAFETY','Keep a close eye on children at all times. The zoo can get very busy, and it\'s easy to lose sight of them, especially near animal enclosures and play areas.','Gemini (Paris Zoo)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:37:53'),(100,18,'SAFETY','Follow all instructions and warnings provided by zoo staff and on signs. Never attempt to feed or touch the animals, as this can be dangerous for both you and the animals.','Gemini (Paris Zoo)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:37:53'),(101,18,'INSIDER','Check the zoo\'s schedule online for feeding times and special events. These can be fantastic opportunities to see the animals at their most active.','Gemini (Paris Zoo)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:37:53'),(102,18,'INSIDER','The best photo opportunities are often found in the early morning or late afternoon when the light is softer and the crowds are thinner. Aim for these times to capture stunning shots of the animals.','Gemini (Paris Zoo)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:37:53'),(103,18,'INSIDER','Consider purchasing tickets online in advance to avoid long queues at the entrance, especially during peak season. This will save you valuable time and allow you to start exploring sooner.','Gemini (Paris Zoo)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:37:53'),(104,18,'INSIDER','Don\'t miss the \'Grand Rocher\' (Big Rock), it offers panoramic views of the entire zoo and surrounding Bois de Vincennes. It’s a great spot for orientation and stunning photos.','Gemini (Paris Zoo)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:37:53'),(105,18,'INSIDER','Pack a picnic! While there are food options available inside the zoo, bringing your own snacks and lunch can save you money and offer more flexibility during your visit. There are designated picnic areas.','Gemini (Paris Zoo)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:37:53'),(106,18,'INSIDER','Take advantage of the free app or downloadable map of the zoo to plan your route efficiently and locate specific animals or exhibits that you\'re most interested in seeing. This helps avoid wandering aimlessly.','Gemini (Paris Zoo)','attraction','2025-12-11 10:37:53'),(116,10,'SAFETY','Be mindful of your belongings; pickpocketing can occur in crowded tourist attractions like Amaze Amsterdam, especially during peak hours.','Reddit (Amsterdam)','city','2025-12-11 14:36:52'),(117,10,'SAFETY','Amaze Amsterdam is an immersive experience with potentially disorienting lighting and sound. If you have sensory sensitivities or are prone to disorientation, proceed cautiously and consider taking breaks.','Reddit (Amsterdam)','city','2025-12-11 14:36:52'),(118,10,'SAFETY','Amaze Amsterdam can be very crowded, especially during peak season. Stay aware of your surroundings and personal space to avoid accidental bumps or jostling.','Reddit (Amsterdam)','city','2025-12-11 14:36:52'),(119,10,'SAFETY','If visiting Amaze Amsterdam at night, be aware of your surroundings when leaving the attraction and walking back to your accommodation or transportation. Stick to well-lit and populated streets.','Reddit (Amsterdam)','city','2025-12-11 14:36:52'),(120,10,'SAFETY','If you are travelling with children to Amaze Amsterdam, keep a close eye on them as it is easy to get disoriented in such attraction.','Reddit (Amsterdam)','city','2025-12-11 14:36:52'),(121,10,'SAFETY','Consider purchasing tickets online in advance. This not only guarantees entry but can also help you avoid long queues, which can expose you to potential petty theft.','Reddit (Amsterdam)','city','2025-12-11 14:36:52'),(122,10,'INSIDER','Check Amaze Amsterdam\'s website for special events or themed nights that might enhance your experience.','Reddit (Amsterdam)','city','2025-12-11 14:36:52'),(123,10,'INSIDER','Consider visiting Amaze Amsterdam during off-peak hours (e.g., weekdays or early mornings) for a less crowded and more immersive experience, allowing you to fully appreciate the exhibits without being overwhelmed.','Reddit (Amsterdam)','city','2025-12-11 14:36:52'),(124,10,'INSIDER','Since Amaze Amsterdam is located in Amsterdam, be sure to use local public transportation to get to the location, as trains go just about anywhere every ten minutes from Amsterdam central station.','Reddit (Amsterdam)','city','2025-12-11 14:36:52');
